@startuml Voice_Command_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Idle : App Started

Idle --> Listening : User Activates Voice Command
Listening --> Processing : Speech Recognized
Processing --> Executing : Command Matched
Executing --> Feedback : Function Executed
Feedback --> Idle : Complete

Listening --> ContinuousMode : User Activates Continuous
ContinuousMode --> Listening : User Input Received
ContinuousMode --> SleepMode : 30s Silence
SleepMode --> ContinuousMode : Voice Wake-up
ContinuousMode --> Idle : User Exits

Processing --> Feedback : Command Not Found


@enduml
